node.text: Let me tell ya bout my best frannn😍 HAPPY BIRTHDAY🎂🎉 to my childhood partner in crime since day 1🤣 until forever! People pray for a friend like you but God blessed me with you as my sister🙏🏼 I hope everyone has someone in their lives who is just as supportive, good hearted, caring, funny and pure as you are Chrissy🥰 @christinemelanie_ I LOVE YOU!
